#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced &sheets;"
msgstr "Napredni &sheets;"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Series"
msgstr "Nizovi"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When constructing a spreadsheet you often need to include a series of "
"values, such as 10, 11, 12..., in a row or column. There are several ways "
"you can do this in &sheets;."
msgstr ""
"Pri kreiranju tabele često je potrebno uključiti niz vrijednosti, kao na "
"primjer 10,11,12 ..., u redu ili koloni. Postoji više načina kako ovo "
"uraditi u &sheets;."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a simple short series such as 5, 6, 7, 8... the <quote>Drag and Copy </"
"quote> method is the simplest. Enter the starting value into the starting "
"cell and the next value of the series into an adjacent cell. Then select "
"both cells and move the mouse pointer so that it is over the small square at "
"the bottom right corner; the cursor will change to a diagonal double headed "
"arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while "
"you drag the cells down or across as needed."
msgstr ""
"Za jednostavane nizove kao na primjer 5,6,7,8... <quote>Prevuci i kopiraj </"
"quote> metod je najjednostavniji. Unesite početnu vrijednost u početnu "
"ćeliju i slijedeću vrijednost niza u narednu ćeliju. Zatim pomjerite kursor "
"miša u donji desni ugao iznad malog kvadratića; kursor će se promjeniti u "
"duplu dijagonalnu strelicu. Zatim držite <mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> "
"tipku miša pritisnutom dok prevlačite ćelije dole ili u stranu po potrebi."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The step size is calculated as the difference between the two starting "
"values that you have entered. For example if you enter <userinput>4</"
"userinput> into cell A1 and <userinput>3.5</userinput> into A2 then select "
"both cells and Drag and Copy them down, the step size will be the value in "
"A2 minus the value in A1, -0.5 in this case so you will get the series 4, "
"3.5, 3, 2.5, 2..."
msgstr ""
"Veličina koraka se računa kao razlika izmeđ dvije početne vrijednosti koje "
"ste unijeli. Na primjer ako unesete  <userinput>4</userinput> u ćeliju A1 i  "
"<userinput>3.5</userinput> u A2 i označite obje ćelije i Prevučete i "
"kopirate ih, veličina koraka će biti vrijednost iz A2 minus vrijednost iz "
"A1, -0.5 u ovom slučaju, pa će niz biti 4, 3.5, 3, 2.5, 2..."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method will even cope with series where the "
"step value is not a constant value but is itself a series. So that if you "
"start with 1, 3, 4, 6 Drag and Copy will extend it to 1, 3, 4, 6, 7, 9, 10, "
"12..., the step value in this example being the series 2, 1, 2, 1..."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Prevuci i kopiraj</quote> metoda će raditi i sa nizovima gdje "
"vrijednost koraka nije konstantna već je i sama niz.. Tako da ako počnete sa "
"nizom 1, 3, 4, 6 Prevuci i kopiraj će ga nastaviti kao 1, 3, 4, 6, 7, 9, 10, "
"12..., vrijednost koraka u ovom nizu je data kao 2, 1, 2, 1..."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also recognizes some special <quote>series</quote> such as the days "
"of the week. Try entering <userinput>Friday</userinput> into a cell (note "
"the capitalization) then Drag and Copy it down. To see what special series "
"are available, and perhaps create your own, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Custom Lists...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"&sheets; također raspoznaje i posebne vrste nizova <quote>nizovi</quote> kao "
"što su dani u sedmici. Pokušajte unijeti <userinput>Petak</userinput> u "
"ćeliju (pazite na velika slova) onda je Prevucite i kopirajte. Da vidite "
"koje su posebni nizovi dostupni, i možda kreirate i vlastiti niz, odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Posebne liste...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a cell and choose <guimenuitem>Series...</guimenuitem> from "
"the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu you will see the <guilabel>Series</"
"guilabel> dialog box. This is useful for creating series that are too long "
"to be conveniently constructed using the Drag and Copy method, or for "
"creating geometric series such as 1, 1.5, 2.25, 3.375... where the step "
"value, 1.5 in this case, is used as a multiplier."
msgstr ""
"Ako odaberete ćeliu i izaberete <guimenuitem>Nizovi...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu> menija vidjeti ćete <guilabel>Nizovi</guilabel> "
"dijaloški okvir. Ovo je korisno kod kreiranja nizova koji su previše dugi da "
"bi bila korištena metoda Prevuci i kopiraj, ili za kreiranje geometrijskih "
"nizova kao na primjer 1, 1.5, 2.25, 3.375... gdje je veličina koraka, 1.5 u "
"ovom slučaju, korištena za kao množitelj."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the type of series that you want is too complicated for any of the "
"previous methods, consider using a formula and Drag and Copying that. For "
"example to create a series with the values 2, 4, 16, 256... enter "
"<userinput>2</userinput> into A1, <userinput>=A1*A1</userinput> into A2, and "
"Drag and Copy cell A2 down."
msgstr ""
"Ako je tip niza koji želite previše komplikovan za neku od prehodnih metoda, "
"razmotrite korištenje formle i Prevuci i kopiranja iste. Na primjer da "
"kreirate niz sa vrijednostima 2,4,16, 256 ... unesite  <userinput>2</"
"userinput> u A1, <userinput>=A1*A1</userinput> u A2, i Prevucite i kopirajte "
"A2 ćeliju."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Formulae"
msgstr "Formule"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Built in Functions"
msgstr "Ugrađene funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; has a huge range of built in mathematical and other <link linkend="
"\"functions\">functions</link> that can be used in a formula cell. They can "
"be seen and accessed by selecting a cell then choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> "
"menu. This brings up the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; ima veliki broj ugrađenih i matematičkih <link linkend=\"functions"
"\">funkcija</link> koje se mogu koristiti u formuli. Mogu se pogledati i "
"može im se pristupiti preko <guimenuitem>Funkcija...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<guimenu>Dodaj</guimenu> menija. Ovo prikazuje <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> "
"dialoški okvir."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the function you want to use from the listbox at the left of the "
"dialog box. The <guilabel>Help</guilabel> tab page will then display a "
"description, the return type, Syntax, Parameters, and Examples for this "
"function. In addition this page provides often links to Related Functions. "
"Then press the button with the down arrow key symbol on it to paste it into "
"the text edit box at the bottom of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite funkciju koji želite koristiti sa date liste u lijevom dijelu "
"dijaloškog okvira. <guilabel>Pomoć</guilabel> kartica će prikazati opis, "
"povratni tip, sintaksu, parametre, i primjere za ovu funkciju. U nastavku "
"ove stranice  prikazani su često korišteni linkov za Povezane funkcije. "
"Zatim pritisnite tipku sa strelicom dole  da biste zalijepili sadržaj  u "
"okvir za uređivanje teksta na dnu okvira."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> tab page will then be displayed to let "
"you enter the parameter(s) for the function you have just chosen. If you "
"want to enter an actual value for a parameter, just type it into the "
"appropriate text box in the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page. To enter a "
"cell reference rather than a value, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on "
"the appropriate text box in the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page; then "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the target cell in the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Parameteri</guilabel> kartica će biti prikazana kako biste mogli "
"unijeti parametre za funkciju koju ste odabrali. Ako želite unijeti stvarnu "
"vrijednost parametra, samo je ukucajte u odgovarajući tekstualni okvir u "
"<guilabel>Parameteri</guilabel> stranici. Za unos reference ćelije umjesto "
"vrijednosti, <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> pritisnite na odgovarajući "
"tekstualni okvir u <guilabel>Parameteri</guilabel> stranici; zatim "
"<mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik na željenu ćeliju u radnoj stranici.."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of using the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page, cell references "
"such as <userinput>B6</userinput> can be entered by typing them directly "
"into the edit box at the bottom of the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog. "
"If a function has more than one parameter separate them with a semi-colon "
"(<keysym>;</keysym>)."
msgstr ""
"Umjesto korištenja <guilabel>Parameteri</guilabel> stranice, reference "
"ćelije kao <userinput>B6</userinput> mogu biti unešene i ukucavanjem istih "
"direktno u okvir za uređivanje na dnu <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> okvira. "
"Ako funkcija ima više od jednog parametra potrebno ih je razdvojiti tačka "
"zarezom (<keysym>;</keysym>)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button will insert the function into "
"the current cell and close the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom <guibutton>OK</guibutton> tipke unijecete funkciju u trenutnu "
"ćeliju i zatvoriti <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> okvir."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can of course do without the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog and "
"simply type the complete expression into the main text entry box in the "
"<guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> tool options. Function names are not case "
"sensitive. Do not forget that all expressions must start with an <keysym>=</"
"keysym> symbol."
msgstr ""
"Ovo možete uraditi i bez <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> okvira i jednostavno "
"ukucati cijeli izraz u glavni tekstualni okvir u <guilabel>Uređivač ćelija</"
"guilabel> alatne opcije. Imena funkcija nisu osjetljiva na velika i mala "
"slova. Ne zaboravite da svi izrazi moraju započeti sa <keysym>=</keysym> "
"simbolom."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logical Comparisons"
msgstr "Logička poređenja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Logical functions such as IF(), AND(), OR() take parameters which have the "
"logical (boolean) values True or False. This type of value can be produced "
"by other logical functions such as ISEVEN() or by the comparison of values "
"in spreadsheet cells using the comparison expressions given in the following "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Logičke funkcije kao IF(), AND(), OR() primaju parametre koji nisu "
"logičke(bool) vrijednosti Tačno ili Netačno. Ovaj tip vrijednosti može biti "
"kreiran od strane druge logičke funkcije kao ISEVEN() ili poređenjem "
"vrijednosti unutar ćelija u radnoj stranici korištenjem izraza za poređenje "
"datih u slijedećoj tabeli."

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expression"
msgstr "Izraz"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primjer"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>=</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>=</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is equal to"
msgstr "Je jednak"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2==B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is equal to the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2==B3</userinput> je tačan ako je vrijednost u A2 jednaka "
"vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>!</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>!</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:129 advanced.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is not equal to"
msgstr "Nije jednak"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2!=B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is not equal to the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2!=B3</userinput> je tačan ako vrijednost u  A2 nije jednaka "
"vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>&gt;</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>&gt;</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same as <userinput>A2!=B3</userinput>"
msgstr "Isto kao <userinput>A2!=B3</userinput>"

#. Tag: keysym
#: advanced.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;"
msgstr "&lt;"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is less than"
msgstr "Je manji od"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is less than the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;B3</userinput> je tačan ako je vrijednost u A2 manja od "
"vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is less than or equal to"
msgstr "Je manji ili jednak"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;=B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is less than or "
"equal to the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;=B3</userinput> je tačan ako je vrijednost u A2 manja ili "
"jednaka od vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: keysym
#: advanced.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gt;"
msgstr "&gt;"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is greater than"
msgstr "Je veći od"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is greater than "
"the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;B3</userinput> je tačan ako je vrijedost u A2 veća od "
"vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&gt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&gt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is greater than or equal to"
msgstr "Je veći ili jednak"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;=B3</userinput> is True if the value A2 is greater than or "
"equal to the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;=B3</userinput> je tačan ako je vrijedost u A2 veća ili "
"jednaka od vrijednosti u B3"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thus if you enter <userinput>=IF(B3&gt;B1;\"BIGGER\";\"\")</userinput> into "
"a cell it will display BIGGER if the value in B3 is greater than that in B1, "
"otherwise the cell will show nothing."
msgstr ""
"Sko unesete <userinput>=IF(B3&gt;B1;\"BIGGER\";\"\")</userinput> u ćeliju "
"prikazati će se BIGGER ako je vrijednost u  B3 veća od vrijednosti u ćeliji "
"B1, u suprotnom neće biti prikazano ništa."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Absolute Cell References"
msgstr "O referencama poziva"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a formula contains a cell reference that reference will normally be "
"changed when the cell is copied to another part of the worksheet. To prevent "
"this behavior put a <keysym>$</keysym> symbol before the column letter, row "
"number or both."
msgstr ""
"Ako formula sadrži referencu na ćeliju ta referenca će biti promijenjena "
"kada je ćelija kopirana u drugi dio radne sveske. Da spriječite ovo stavite "
"<keysym>$</keysym> simbol prije slova kolone, broja reda ili oboje."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=D5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=E6</userinput> (the normal behavior)."
msgstr ""
"Ako A1 sadrži formulu <userinput>=D5</userinput> onda će to pri kopiranju  "
"B2 postati<userinput>=E6</userinput> (normalno ponašanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=$D5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=D6</userinput> (column letter not "
"changed)."
msgstr ""
"Ako A1 sadrži formulu <userinput>=$D5</userinput> onda će to pri kopiranju  "
"B2 postati<userinput>=D6</userinput> (slovo kolone nepromijenjeno)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=D$5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=E5</userinput> (row number not "
"changed)."
msgstr ""
"Ako A1 sadrži formulu <userinput>=D$5</userinput> onda će to pri kopiranju  "
"B2 postati<userinput>=E5</userinput> (broj reda nepromijenjen)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=$D$5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will remain as <userinput>=D5</userinput> (neither the column "
"letter nor the row number are changed)."
msgstr ""
"Ako A1 sadrži formulu <userinput>=$D$5</userinput> onda će to pri kopiranju  "
"ostati<userinput>=D5</userinput> (slovo kolone nepromijenjeno i broj reda "
"nepromijenjen)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are entering or editing a cell reference in a formula the shortcut "
"key <keysym>F4</keysym> can be used to step through these four possibilities."
msgstr ""
"Kada unosite ili uređujete referencu ćelije u formuli tipka kratice "
"<keysym>F4</keysym> može biti korištena za kretanje kroz ove četiri "
"mogućnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"namedareas\">Named cells</link> can be used in a similar way "
"to include a unchanging cell reference in a formula."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"namedareas\">Imenovane ćelije</link> može biti korišteno na "
"isti način da se ukljči nemijenjanje reference ćelije u formuli."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arithmetic using Special Paste"
msgstr "Aritmetika korištenja specijalnog lijepljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you may want to add a single value to a number of cells, or "
"subtract a value from them, or multiply or divide them all by a single "
"value. The <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</guimenuitem> option lets you do "
"this quickly and easily."
msgstr ""
"Ponekad ćete željeti dodati jedinstvenu vrijednost određenom broju ćelija, "
"ili oduzeti vrijednost od njih, ili ih pomnožiti ili podijeliti istom "
"vrijednošću.<guimenuitem>Specijalno lijepljenje...</guimenuitem> opcija "
"dozvoljava da se ovo uradi brzo i lako."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, enter the modifier value into any spare cell on your spreadsheet and "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> it. Then select the area of cells you want "
"to change, choose <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> or the context menu and select <guilabel>Addition</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Subtraction</guilabel>, <guilabel>Multiplication</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Division</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Operation</"
"guilabel> section of the dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Prvo, unesite vrijednost modifikacije u bilo koju praznu ćeliju i "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> te je. Onda odaberite dio ćelija koje "
"želite promijeniti i odaberite <guimenuitem>Specijalno lijepljenje...</"
"guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> ili  iz dodatak menija "
"<guilabel>Dodavanje</guilabel>, <guilabel>Oduzimanje</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Množenje</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Dijeljenje</guilabel> iz "
"<guilabel>Operacije</guilabel> dijela dijaloškog okvira."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also apply different modifier values to different rows or columns of "
"the target area by copying an area containing the wanted modifiers before "
"selecting the target area and doing <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem> For example, if you enter <userinput>5</userinput> into cell "
"A1, <userinput>10</userinput> into B1, select both cells and do a "
"<guimenuitem> Copy</guimenuitem> then <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem> <guilabel> Addition</guilabel> into cells A10 to D15, 5 will be "
"added to A10:A15 and C10:C15, and 10 to B10:B15 and D10:D15."
msgstr ""
"Možete također primjeniti različite vrijednosti modifikatora za redove i "
"kolone željenog područja kopiranjem područja sa željenim modifikatorom prije "
"odabira željenog područja i korištenja <guimenuitem>Specijalnog "
"lijepljenja...</guimenuitem> Na primjer, ako unesete <userinput>5</"
"userinput> u ćeliju A1, <userinput>10</userinput> u B1, odaberete obje "
"ćelije i pritisnete <guimenuitem> Kopiraj</guimenuitem> zatim "
"<guimenuitem>Specijalno lijepljenje...</guimenuitem> <guilabel> Sabiranje</"
"guilabel> u ćelije A10 do D15, 5 će biti dodato ćelijama A10:A15 i C10:C15, "
"i 10 ćelijama B10:B15 i D10:D15."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that a modifier value can be a formula as well as a simple numeric "
"value. If it is a formula then &sheets; will adjust the cell references as "
"for a normal <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> operation."
msgstr ""
"Primjetite da vrijednost modofikatora može biti i formula kao i numerička "
"vrijednost. Ako je formula onda će &sheets; prilagoditi reference ćelije kao "
"normalne za operaciju <guimenuitem>Zalijepi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Array Formulas"
msgstr "Formule u navodnicima"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; allows you to use formulas whose result is a matrix or a range of "
"values. Normally, only the first value is displayed in a cell. If you would "
"like to display the entire matrix, simply use <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;&Enter;</"
"keycombo> when editing a formula, and it will be converted into an array "
"formula, occupying neighboring cells as needed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; dozvoljava da koristite formule čiji je rezultat matrica ili opseg "
"vrijednosti. Normalno, samo je prva vrijednost prikazana u ćeliji. Ako "
"želite prikazati cijelu matricu, jednostavno koristite <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"&Enter;</keycombo> kada uređujete formulu, i biće pretvorena u formulu sa "
"navodnicima, zauzimajući i susjedne ćelije ako je potrebno."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cells that are a part of an array formula are locked for editing."
msgstr ""
"Ćelije koje su dio formule  sa navodnicima su zaključane za uređivanje."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Goal Seeking"
msgstr "Traženje cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can be used to solve algebraic expressions such as <emphasis> x + "
"x^2 = 4</emphasis> or <emphasis>For what value of x does x + x squared equal "
"4 ?</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"&sheets; može biti korišten za riješavanje algebarskih izraza kao  "
"<emphasis> x + x^2 = 4</emphasis>  ili <emphasis>Za koju vrijednost x "
"vrijedi da je  x + x na kvadrat = 4 ?</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For this example you could enter <userinput>=A2+A2*A2</userinput> into A1 "
"then either try different values in A2 until the result in A1 is as close as "
"you wish to <emphasis>4</emphasis> or, preferably, use &sheets;'s "
"<guimenuitem>Goal Seek...</guimenuitem> feature which automatically adjusts "
"the value in one cell to try to make the value in another cell as close as "
"possible to a target value."
msgstr ""
"Za ovaj primjer možete unijeti <userinput>=A2+A2*A2</userinput> u A1 onda "
"probati druge vrijednosti u A2 dok rezultat u A1 ne bude blizu željenog "
"broja <emphasis>4</emphasis> ili koristite &sheets;'-ov <guimenuitem>Traži "
"cilj...</guimenuitem> dodatak koji automatski prilagodi vrijednost u jednoj "
"ćeliji da dobije vrijednost u drugoj ćeliji ili ako je moguće željenu "
"vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is invoked by selecting <guimenuitem>Goal Seek...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. This brings up a dialog box in which you "
"should enter the reference of the target value cell (<userinput>A1</"
"userinput> in this case) into the <guilabel>Set cell:</guilabel> box, the "
"target value itself (<userinput>4</userinput>) into the <guilabel>To value:</"
"guilabel> box and the reference of the cell that is to be changed "
"(<userinput>A2</userinput>) into the <guilabel>By changing cell:</guilabel> "
"box. Note that you need to have entered some initial value into the cell "
"that is to be changed before starting <guimenuitem>Goal Seek</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Poziva se odabirom <guimenuitem>Traži cilj...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<guimenu>Podaci</guimenu> menija. Ovo prikazuje okvir u kojem trebate "
"unijeti referencu željene vrijednosti ćelije (<userinput>A1</userinput> u "
"ovom slučaju) u <guilabel>Podesi ćeliju:</guilabel> okvir, željenu "
"vrijednost (<userinput>4</userinput>) u <guilabel>Tražena vrijednost:</"
"guilabel> okvir i referenca ćelije koju treba promijeniti (<userinput>A2</"
"userinput>) u <guilabel>Ćelija za izmjenu:</guilabel> okvir. Primjetite da "
"trebate unijeti neke početne vrijednosti u ćeliju koju treba mijenjati prije "
"početka <guimenuitem>Traženja cilja</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button will start the calculation. "
"When it finishes and if it has found a solution press the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button to accept the result or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to "
"keep the original value."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom <guibutton>OK</guibutton> tioke započinje računanje. Kada završi "
"ako ste pronašli riješenje pritisnite <guibutton>OK</guibutton> tipku da "
"prihvatite rezultat ili <guibutton>Poništi</guibutton> da zadržite "
"dosadašnju vrijednost."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot Tables"
msgstr "Pivot tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can be used to construct <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Pivot_table\">pivot tables</ulink> using the data of the current table."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; može biti korišten za kreiranje <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Pivot_table\">pivot tabele</ulink> korištenjem podataka iz trenutne "
"tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature can be invoked by selecting <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> "
"from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. Below is an example of pivot table "
"generation."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dodatak se koristi izborom <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<guimenu>Podaci</guimenu> menija. Ispod je primjer generisanja pivot tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supposing we have the following data."
msgstr "Pod pretpostavkom da imamo slijedeće podatke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initial table"
msgstr "Početna tabela."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We want to create a pivot table of our choice and requirement. So we choose "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Data</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Želimo kreirati tabelu sa našim izborima i zahtjevima. Tako da izaberemo "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Podaci</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog box that will appear allows user to select the source of data. "
"The data can be taken from the current worksheet or from an external source "
"like a database or <abbrev>ODS</abbrev> file."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj okvir će se prikazati da korisnik unese izvor podataka. Podaci mogu "
"biti preuzeti iz trenutne radne stranice ili vanjske baze podataka kao "
"<abbrev>ODS</abbrev> dokument."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the data source"
msgstr "Izbor izvora podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is the dialog box which allows the user to customize the pivot table. "
"The column labels in the source data are converted to labels which serve as "
"the working fields. The labels can be dragged and dropped into one of three "
"areas (<guilabel>Rows</guilabel>, <guilabel>Columns</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Values</guilabel>) to generate the pivot table. You can reset your "
"choices using <guibutton>Reset DnD</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje je okvir koji dozvoljava korisniku da uredi pivot tabelu. Oznake "
"kolona u izvoru podataka su pretvorene u oznake koje služe kao radna polja. "
"Oznake mogu biti premještane i spuštane u jedno od područja "
"(<guilabel>Redovi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Kolone</guilabel> ili "
"<guilabel>Vrijednosti</guilabel>) da generišete pivot tabelu. Možete "
"poništiti vaše izbore korištenjem <guibutton>Poništi DnD</guibutton> tipku."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot table customization dialog"
msgstr "Okvir za uređivanje pivot tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In our example, <replaceable>Name</replaceable> is dragged to "
"<guilabel>Rows</guilabel>, <replaceable>Category</replaceable> to "
"<guilabel>Columns</guilabel>, <replaceable>Score</replaceable> to "
"<guilabel>Values</guilabel>. User defined functions like sum, average, max, "
"min, count, &etc; can be selected from the <guilabel>Select Option</"
"guilabel> list."
msgstr ""
"U našem primjeru <replaceable>Ime</replaceable> je prevučeno u "
"<guilabel>Redove</guilabel>, <replaceable>Kategoriju</replaceable> u "
"<guilabel>Kolone</guilabel>, <replaceable>Rezultat</replaceable> u "
"<guilabel>Vrijednosti</guilabel>. Korisnički definirane funkcije kao, suma, "
"prosjek, maksimum, minimum, broji, &itd; mogu biti odabrane u  "
"<guilabel>Odaberi opciju</guilabel> listi."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Add Filter</guibutton> button can be used to open filter "
"dialog box to filter the desired data. Using this box you can define "
"multiple filters based on the column label and the relationship between them "
"(<guimenuitem>And</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Or</guimenuitem>). This "
"would allow extreme freedom to customize the output."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Dodaj filter</guibutton> tipka može biti korištena za otvaranje "
"okvira za izbor filtera datih podataka. Korištenjem ovog okvira možete "
"definisati više filtera zasnovanih na oznakama kolona i veza među njima  "
"(<guimenuitem>I</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Ili</guimenuitem>). Ovo će "
"dozvoliti veliku slobodu pri uređivanju izlaza."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot table filtering dialog"
msgstr "Okvir za filtriranje pivot tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Total Rows</guilabel> and <guilabel>Total Columns</guilabel>: "
"checking these allow automatic totalling of corresponding rows and columns "
"in the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ukupno redova</guilabel> i <guilabel>Ukupno kolona</guilabel>: "
"označavanje ovih vam omogućava automatsko sumiranje odgovarajućih redova i "
"kolona u pivot tabeli."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using more than one Worksheet"
msgstr "Korištenje više od jedne Radne stranice"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start a new, empty, document with &sheets; it will create a number "
"of blank worksheets. The number of sheets it creates is determined by the "
"selected template."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete novi prazan dokument sa &sheets; kreira broj praznih radnih "
"listova. Broj stranica koje su kreirane je određen odabranim predloškom."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sheet</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> will add another sheet to the document."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Umetni</guimenu><guimenuitem>List</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> će dodati novi list u dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also switch between worksheets by using the <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keysym>PgDown</keysym></keycombo> to move to the next sheet, "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>PgUp</keysym></keycombo> to move to "
"the previous one."
msgstr ""
"Promjenu među stranicama možete vršiti pomoću <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Stranica dole</keysym></keycombo> za prebacivanje na "
"slijedeći list, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Stranica gore</"
"keysym></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Worksheets are given the default names of <emphasis>Sheet1</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Sheet2</emphasis>... You can give a sheet a different name by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the tab and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Rename Sheet...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"Radni listovi su dati zadanim imenima <emphasis>List1</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>List2</emphasis>... List možete imenovati drugačije korištenjem "
"<mousebutton>desnog</mousebutton> pritiska na karticu i izborom "
"<guimenuitem>Preimenuj list...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a sheet from the document use the <guimenuitem>Remove Sheet </"
"guimenuitem> option in the context menu that pops up when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the tab for the sheet you want to "
"remove."
msgstr ""
"Da uklonite list iz dokumenta koristite <guimenuitem> Ukloni list </"
"guimenuitem> opciju u meniju koji se pojavi pri <mousebutton>desnom</"
"mousebutton> pritisku na karticu lista koji želite ukloniti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other entries in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> "
"Sheet</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu allow you to show or hide a sheet in "
"much the same way as rows and columns can be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ostali unosi u <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> List</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> podmeniju dozvoljavaju vam prikaz sakrivanja lista "
"na sličan način kao i redova i kolona."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want a formula in one sheet to refer to a cell in another sheet, the "
"cell reference must start with the sheet name followed by an exclamation "
"mark (<keysym>!</keysym>). For example if you enter <userinput>=Sheet2!A2 </"
"userinput> into a cell in Sheet 1, that cell will take the value from A2 of "
"Sheet2. Note that sheet names are case sensitive."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da formula u jednom lisu referencira na ćeliju u drugom listu, "
"poziv reference mora biti praćen uzvičnikom (<keysym>!</keysym>). Na primjer "
"ako unesete <userinput>=Sheet2!A2 </userinput> u ćeliju u Listu 1, ta ćelija "
"će imati vrijednost iz A2 Lista 2. Imena listova su osjetljiva na veličinu "
"slova."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consolidating Data"
msgstr "Objedinjavanje podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may have constructed a document containing several worksheets containing "
"similar data but for, say, different months of the year, and wish to have "
"summary sheet containing the consolidated (&eg;, sum or average) values of "
"the corresponding data items in the other sheets."
msgstr ""
"Možda ste kreirali dokument koji sadrži više radnih listova koji sadrže "
"slične podatke recimo za različite mjesece u godini i želite imati list sa "
"sažetkom koji sadrži sažete vrijednosti(&npr; suma ili prosjek) "
"odgovarajućih podataka u listovima."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This task can be made slightly easier by using the <guimenuitem> "
"Consolidate...</guimenuitem> item from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se može lakše uraditi korištenjem <guimenuitem> Objedini...</"
"guimenuitem> stavke iz <guimenu>Podaci</guimenu> menija."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option brings up the <guilabel>Consolidate</guilabel> dialog "
"box."
msgstr ""
"Izborom ove opcije otvara se <guimenuitem> Objedini...</guimenuitem> okvir."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each of the source sheets, enter a reference to the desired data area in "
"the <guilabel>Reference:</guilabel> box. Press <guibutton>Add</guibutton> to "
"transfer it to the <guilabel>Entered references:</guilabel> box. The "
"reference should include the name of the sheet containing the source data, "
"such as <userinput>January!A1:A10</userinput>, and can be entered "
"automatically by selecting the area in the appropriate sheet."
msgstr ""
"Za svaki od izvornih listova, unesite referencu za odabrano područje "
"podataka u <guilabel>Referenca:</guilabel> okvir. Pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> da ih prebacite u <guilabel>Unijete reference:</"
"guilabel> okvir. Reference bi trebale uključivati ime lista koji sadrži "
"izvorne podatke, kao što je  <userinput>Januar!A1:A10</userinput>, i mogu "
"biti unesene automatski odabirom područja u odgovarajućem listu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After entering the references for all of the source data sheets select the "
"cell in the target sheet where you want the top left corner of the "
"consolidated results to appear. Then choose the appropriate function from "
"the <guilabel>Function:</guilabel> combo box and press the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Nakon unosa referenci za sve izvorne listove podataka odaberite ćeliju u "
"željenom listu gdje želite da bude gornji lijevi ugao objedinjenih "
"rezultata. Onda odaberite odgovarajuću funkciju za aproksimaciju iz "
"<guilabel>Funkcija:</guilabel> okvira i pritisnite <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the <guibutton>Details >></guibutton> in the dialog and check "
"the <guilabel>Copy data</guilabel> box the values resulting from the "
"consolidation will be placed into the target cells rather than the formulae "
"to calculate them."
msgstr ""
"Ako pritisnete <guibutton>Detalji >></guibutton> u okviru i označite "
"<guilabel>Kopiraj podatke</guilabel> okvir rezultati objedinjavanja će biti "
"smješteni u željene ćelije umjesto formula za njihov izračun."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting a Chart"
msgstr "Ubacivanje grafikona"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert a chart into a sheet to give a graphical view of your data."
msgstr "Možete ubaciti grafikon u list da date grafički prikaz vaših podataka."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First enable <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker using the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dockers</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Prvo omogućite <guilabel>Dodaj oblik</guilabel> doker korištenjem "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dokeri</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> meni stavke."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then select the area of cells containing the data and choose "
"<guilabel>Chart</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel>. Drag the "
"cursor across the sheet while holding the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"mouse button down to define the area where you want the chart to appear, "
"there is no need to be too accurate at this stage as the chart size can "
"easily be changed at any time. When you release the mouse button a "
"<guilabel>Chart Options</guilabel> dialog box will appear."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite područje ćelija koje sadrži podatke i odaberite "
"<guilabel>Grafikon</guilabel> u <guilabel>Dodaj oblik</guilabel>. Prevucite "
"pokazivač preko lista dok držite <mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> tipku "
"miša pritisnutom da odaberete područje gdje želite da se pojavi grafikon, "
"nema potrebe da budete precizni u ovom dijelu jer se veličina grafikona može "
"promijeniti u bilo kom trenutku. Kada pustite tipku miša <guilabel>Opcije "
"grafikona</guilabel> okvir će se prikazati."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data area is already prefilled with the selected cell range. Select the "
"first row and column as labels, check <guilabel>Data set in rows</guilabel> "
"and click the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button. The Dialog will vanish and "
"you will see the chart embedded into the worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Podaci su ispunjeni u odabrani opseg ćelija. Odaberite prvi red i kolonu kao "
"oznake, označite <guilabel>Podaci u redovima</guilabel> i pritisnite "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> tipku. Okvir će nestati i vidjećete grafikon "
"ugrađen u radni list."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:420
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Now select <guibutton>Chart Editing Tool</guibutton> from the "
#| "<guilabel>Tools</guilabel> docker and edit the chart properties like "
#| "chart type, labels and axis in the <guilabel>Tools Options</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"Now select <guibutton>Chart Editing Tool</guibutton> from the "
"<guilabel>Tools</guilabel> docker and edit the chart properties like chart "
"type, labels and axis in the <guilabel>Chart editing</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Sada odaberite <guibutton>Alat za uređivanje grafikona</guibutton> iz "
"<guilabel>Alati</guilabel> dokera i uredite osobine grafikona kao što su "
"tip, oznake i ose u <guilabel>Alatne opcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of embedded chart"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana ugrađenog grafikona"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move, resize or even delete the embedded chart switch to the "
"<guibutton>Basic shape manipulation</guibutton> tool and click anywhere "
"within the chart area. It should now appear with a green border and with a "
"small yellow square at each corner and in the middle of each edge."
msgstr ""
"Da pomjerate promjenite veličinu ili obrišete grafikon idite na "
"<guibutton>Osnovne promjene oblika</guibutton> alat i pritisnite bilo gdje u "
"području grafikona. Sada bi se trebao pojaviti sa zelenim okvirom i sa malim "
"žutim uglom u svakom uglu i na sredini svake ivice."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the cursor over any of the squares it should change to a double "
"headed arrow. You can resize the chart by dragging one of these squares with "
"the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button pressed. To delete the "
"chart <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on one of the squares and "
"select <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ako pomjerite pokazivač preko bilo kojeg ugla trebao bi se promijeniti u "
"duplu strelicu. Možete promijeniti veličinu grafikona povlačenjem jednog od "
"ovih uglova sa pritisnutom <mousebutton>lijevom</mousebutton> tipkom miša. "
"Da obrišete grafikon pritisnite <mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> pritiskom "
"miša na jedan od uglova i odaberete <guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the chart move the cursor into the chart. The cursor should then "
"change to a cross, press the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"and you will be able to drag the chart to where you want it to be."
msgstr ""
"Da pomjerite grafikon pomjerite pokazivač unutar grafikona. Pokazivač bi "
"sada trebao postati križić, pritisnite <mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> "
"tipku miša i moći ćete da pomjerate grafikon gdje god želite."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To restore the chart to its normal appearance simply click anywhere outside "
"of the chart area."
msgstr ""
"Da vratite grafikon u normalni prikaz jednostavno pritisnite bilo gdje van "
"područja grafikona."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:449
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To change the format of the chart itself <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
#| "click twice within the chart area. The chart <guilabel>Tools Options</"
#| "guilabel> should appear in the docker. You can then use these tools to "
#| "change the chart."
msgid ""
"To change the format of the chart itself <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click twice within the chart area. The chart <guilabel>Chart editing</"
"guilabel> should appear in the docker. You can then use these tools to "
"change the chart."
msgstr ""
"Da promijenite format grafikona pritisnite dvaput <mousebutton>lijevom</"
"mousebutton> tipkom miša u području grafikona. Grafikon <guilabel>Alatne "
"opcije</guilabel> ni se trebale prikazati u dokeru. Ove alate možete "
"koristiti za izmjenu grafikona."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting External Data"
msgstr "Ubacivanje vanjskih podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert data from a text file or from the clipboard into a worksheet "
"by first selecting the cell where you want the top left item of the inserted "
"data to appear, then choosing <guimenuitem>From Text File...</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>From Clipboard...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guisubmenu>External Data</guisubmenu> "
"</menuchoice> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Možete ubaciti podatke iz tekstualnog dokumente ili iz međuspremnika u radni "
"list odabiranjem ćelije u kojoj želite da bude gornji lijevi dio ubačenih "
"podataka, a zatim izabiranjem <guimenuitem>Iz tekstualnog dokumenta...</"
"guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Iz međuspremnika...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vanjske podatke</guisubmenu> "
"</menuchoice> podmenija."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In both cases &sheets; will assume that the data is in <acronym>CSV</"
"acronym> form and will open a dialog box allowing you to control how the "
"data is extracted from the file or clipboard and placed into the worksheet "
"cells."
msgstr ""
"U oba slučaja &sheets; će pretpostaviti da su podaci u <acronym>CSV</"
"acronym> formi i otvaraju okvir koji dozvoljava kontrolu kako su podaci "
"isčitani iz dokumenta ili međuspremnika i smješteni u ćelije radnog lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If support for it has been included in your system, &sheets; can also insert "
"data from a <acronym>SQL</acronym> database into a worksheet. This is done "
"by using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guisubmenu> External "
"Data</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Database...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Ako je podrška uključena u sistem &sheets; može učitati podatke iz "
"<acronym>SQL</acronym> baze podataka u radni list. Ovo se obavlja "
"korištenjem <menuchoice><guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu><guisubmenu> Vanjski podaci</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Iz baze podataka...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"opcije."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link Cells"
msgstr "Poveži ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A spreadsheet cell can be linked to an action so that <mousebutton> left </"
"mousebutton> clicking on the cell will, for example, open your browser. To "
"make a cell act in this way select it and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Link...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. This will bring up the <guilabel>Insert Link</guilabel> dialog "
"box, which lets you choose between four types of link:"
msgstr ""
"Tabelarna ćelija može biti povezana naredbom tako da će <mousebutton> lijevi "
"</mousebutton> pritisak na ćeliju na primjer otvoriti vaš pretraživač. Da bi "
"ćelija radila na ovaj način odaberite ćeliju i izaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu><guimenuitem>Link...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Ovo če otvoriti  <guilabel>Ubaci link</guilabel> okvir, koji "
"vam dozvoljava da birate između četiri tipa linka:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An <guilabel>Internet</guilabel> link cell will try to open your default "
"browser at the &URL; entered in the <guilabel>Internet address:</guilabel> "
"text box of the <guilabel>Insert Link</guilabel> dialog when it is clicked. "
"This could be, for example, <userinput>http://www.calligra.org</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Internet</guilabel> link ćelija će pokušati otvoriti u zadanom "
"pretraživaču u &URL; unijetom u <guilabel>Internet adresa:</guilabel> "
"tekstualnom okviru <guilabel>Ubaci link</guilabel> okvir kad je pritisnut. "
"Ovo može biti na primjer, <userinput>http://www.calligra.org</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a cell containing a <guilabel>Mail</guilabel> link will open "
"your email composer using the address entered in the <guilabel>Email:</"
"guilabel> text box as the To: address. For example <userinput>anon@example."
"com</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom na ćeliju koja sadrži  <guilabel>Adresu e-pošte</guilabel> link "
"otvara okvir za sastavljanje poruka korištenjem adrese unešene u "
"<guilabel>Adresa e-pošte:</guilabel> tekstualni okvir kao i u Za: adresa. Na "
"primjer <userinput>anon@example.com</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <guilabel>File</guilabel> link cell holds the path to a file or folder, as "
"entered into the <guilabel>File location:</guilabel> text box, and will try "
"to open that file or folder with a suitable application when clicked on."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dokument</guilabel> link ćelija sadrži put do dokumenta ili "
"foldera, koji je unešen u <guilabel>Lokacija dokumenta:</guilabel> "
"tekstualni okvir, i probaće otvoriti dokument ili folder sa odgovarajućom "
"aplikacijom kad je pritisnuto na nju."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cell</guilabel> type of link cell holds a &sheets; cell "
"reference, entered in the <guilabel>Cell or Named Area</guilabel> text box. "
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on this type of link cell causes "
"&sheets;'s focus to move to the target cell."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ćelija</guilabel> tip linka ćelija sadrži  &sheets; referenca "
"ćelije, unešena u <guilabel>Ćelija ili imenovano područje</guilabel> "
"tekstualni okvir. <mousebutton>Lijevi</mousebutton> clicking pritisak na "
"ovaj tip linka uzrokuje da se fokus &sheets;-a pomjera na željenu ćeliju."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All four types of link cell need some suitable text to be entered into the "
"<guilabel>Text to display</guilabel> field of the <guilabel>Insert Link</"
"guilabel> dialog. This is the text that appears in the cell."
msgstr ""
"Sva četiri tipa linka u ćelijama trebaju tekst da bude unesen u "
"<guilabel>Tekst za prikaz</guilabel> polje u <guilabel>Ubaci link</guilabel> "
"grijač."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validity Checking"
msgstr "Provjera ispravnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can automatically check the validity of entered data against a "
"number of criteria, and pop up a message box if the data is invalid."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; može automatski provjeriti ispravnost unijetih podataka u skladu sa "
"brojem kriterija, i skočnom porukom ako je podatak pogrešan."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, select the cell(s) to be monitored and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Data</guimenu><guimenuitem>Validity...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. This will bring up &sheets;'s <guilabel>Validity</guilabel> "
"dialog box which has three tabbed pages."
msgstr ""
"Da omogućite ovaj dodatak, odaberite ćelije koje želite pratiti i odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Podaci</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ispravnost...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Ovo će prikazati &sheets;-ov "
"<guilabel>Ispravnost</guilabel> okvir sa tri stranice u karticama."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Criteria</guilabel> page select what type of data is to be "
"considered valid from the <guilabel>Allow:</guilabel> combo box list then "
"define the valid range of values by choosing one of the options in the "
"<guilabel>Data:</guilabel> combo box and entering suitable value(s) into one "
"or both of the edit box(es)."
msgstr ""
"U <guilabel>Kriterij</guilabel> stranici odaberite tip podataka koje želite "
"smatrati ispravnim u <guilabel>Dozvoli:</guilabel> kutije sa listom a onda "
"definirajte ispravan okvir vrijednosti izborom jedne od opcija u "
"<guilabel>Podaci:</guilabel> kutiji i unosom odgovarajućih vrijednosti u "
"jednu ili obje kutije za uređivanje."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have done this change to the <guilabel>Error Alert</guilabel> tab. "
"Here you can choose the type of message box (<guimenuitem>Stop</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Warning</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem>) that will appear when an invalid "
"value is entered, and define the message box title and message text."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste ovo uradili promijenite na <guilabel>Upozorenje o greškama</"
"guilabel> karticu. Ovdje možete odabrati tip okvira sa "
"porukom(<guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Upozorenje</"
"guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Informacija</guimenuitem>) koji će se "
"prikazati kad je pogrešna vrijednost unešena, i definira naslov okvira sa "
"porukom i teksta poruke."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that this feature only checks data that you enter into the cell, for a "
"way of checking the results from formulae cells see the <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">Conditional Cell Attributes</link> section of this Handbook."
msgstr ""
"Primjetite da ovaj dodatak samo provjerava podatke koje ste unijeli u "
"ćeliju, za način provjere rezultata iz ćelija sa formulom pogledajte <link "
"linkend=\"formatdata\">Objedinjavanje atributa ćelije</link> odjeljak ovog "
"priručnika."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Protection"
msgstr "Zaštita"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Protection"
msgstr "Zaštita dokumenata"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting the document means that without the password a user cannot add or "
"delete sheets. Document protection does not protect cells."
msgstr ""
"Zaštita dokumenta znači da bez šifre korisnik ne može dodati ili obrisati "
"listove. Zaštita dokumenata ne štiti ćelije."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Document...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> A dialog appears asking you for a password. The "
"<guilabel>Password:</guilabel> strength meter indicates if your password is "
"secure enough. The longer the indicator is, the more secure your password."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti "
"dokument...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Pojavljuje se okvir sa zahtijevom "
"šifre. <guilabel>Šifra:</guilabel> mjeritelj jačine pokazuje koliko je "
"sigurna vaša šifra. Što je indikator duži šifra je bolja."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Protect Document dialog"
msgstr "Okvir za zaštitu dokumenata"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "That password will then be required to unprotect the document."
msgstr "Šifra će biti zahtjevana da se skine zaštita sa dokumenta."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Unprotect Document dialog"
msgstr "Okvir za skidanje zaštite sa dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a document is protected, you may not:"
msgstr "Kad je dokument zaštićen možda nećete moći:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename a sheet"
msgstr "Preimenovati list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a sheet"
msgstr "Ubaciti list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove a sheet"
msgstr "Ukloniti list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide a sheet"
msgstr "Sakriti list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a sheet"
msgstr "Prikazati list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the sheet properties"
msgstr "Vidjeti osobine lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge or dissociate cells"
msgstr "Spojiti ili razdvojiti ćelije"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet protection"
msgstr "Zašititi list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting a sheet means protecting the contents of all protected cells and "
"objects on a sheet. Individual cells or a selection of cells can be "
"unprotected within a protected sheet, see <link linkend=\"cell-protection"
"\">next section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zaštita lista znači zaštitu sadržaja svih zaštićenih ćelija i objekata na "
"listu. Individualne ćelije ili odjeljci ćelija mogu biti nezaštićeni unutar "
"zaštićenog lista, vidjeti <link linkend=\"cell-protection\">slijedeći "
"odjeljak</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To protect a sheet, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A dialog "
"appears asking you for a password. The <guilabel>Password</guilabel> "
"strength meter indicates if your password is secure enough. The longer the "
"indicator is, the more secure will be your password."
msgstr ""
"Da zaštitite list, odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti list...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikazuje "
"se okvir koji traži šifru. <guilabel>Šifra</guilabel> mjeritelj jačine "
"prikazuje da li je vaša šifra dovoljno sigurna. Što je indikator duži to je "
"šifra sigurnija."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "That password will then be required to unprotect the sheet."
msgstr "Zatim će biti tražena šifra za skidanje zaštite sa lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a sheet is protected, you may not:"
msgstr "Kad je list zaštićen možda nećete moći:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert any object or chart"
msgstr "Umetnuti bilo koji objekat ili grafikon"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format any cell"
msgstr "Formatirati bilo koju ćeliju"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a row or a column"
msgstr "Ubaciti red ili kolonu"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit and change cell content"
msgstr "Urediti ili promijeniti sadržaj ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change any content in the sheet"
msgstr "Promijeniti bilo koji sadržaj lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting a sheet is especially useful for preventing accidental erasure of "
"formulae."
msgstr ""
"Zaštita lista je posebno korisna za spriječavanje slučajnih brisanja formula."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell or selected cells protection"
msgstr "Zaštita ćelije ili odabranih ćelija"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cell protection is active for all cells by default and is effective when you "
"enable sheet protection. So if you keep the default and if you protect the "
"sheet, all cells will be protected."
msgstr ""
"Zaštita ćelije je zadano aktivna za sve ćelije i uključena kad omogućite "
"zaštitu lista. Ako zadržite zadano i zaštitite list, sve ćelije su zaštićene."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want only certain cells to be protected, this default protection must "
"be turned off for all other cells. For example you might want most cells to "
"accept user input so you will uncheck <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> for "
"those and choose to keep protected cells that should stay unchanged (such as "
"titles). So you need 3 steps in order to protect only some cells: unprotect "
"all the cells, select the cells to protect and protect them and then protect "
"the whole sheet."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite zaštititi samo određene ćelije, zadanu zaštitu morate isključiti "
"za sve ostale ćelije. Na primjer možda želite zaštititi većinu ćelija osim "
"onih za korisnikov unos tako da odznačite <guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> za "
"njih i izaberete zadrži zaštićeno ćelije koje trebaju ostati nepromijenjene "
"(kao naslovi). Tako da trebate 3 koraka u cilju zaštite samo nekih ćelija: "
"skinuti zaštitu sa svih, odabrati one koje želite zaštititi i zaštitite ih i "
"zaštitite cijeli list."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "To unprotect all the cells:"
msgstr "Za skodanje zaštite sa svih ćelija:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the entire spreadsheet with the mouse."
msgstr "Označite cijeli list mišem."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the menubar, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"U traci sa menijima odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Format ćelije...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:655 advanced.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog that appears, go to the <guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"U okviru koji se pojavi idite na <guilabel>Zaštita ćelije</guilabel> karticu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and uncheck <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> to remove the protection on all cells. The cells are now all "
"unprotected."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> i odznačite <guilabel>Zaštićeno</"
"guilabel> da uklonite zaštitu sa svih ćelija. Sve ćelije su sada nezaštićene."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To protect a range of selected cells or a selection of non-contiguous cells:"
msgstr "Da zaštitite dio ćelija ili dijela nesusjednih ćelija:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Highlight the range of cells that are to be protected or use the <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key to select non-contiguous cells."
msgstr ""
"Označite opseg ćelija koje treba zaštititi ili koristite <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> tipku za odabir nesusjednih ćelija."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all of the desired cells are selected, go to the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Kada su sve željene ćelije odabrane idite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Formatiraj ćeliju...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the box next to <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> then click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite na okvir do <guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> i pritisnite "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the cells are marked for protection, the protection option must be "
"enabled at the sheet level, that means you must protect the entire sheet for "
"the cell to be effectively protected:"
msgstr ""
"Kada su ćelije označene za zaštitu, opcija zaštite mora biti omogućena na "
"nivou lista, što znači da morate zaštiti cijeli list da bi ćelije zaista "
"bile zaštićene:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti list...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog that appears, provide a safe password, then confirm it by "
"typing it again. Click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"U okviru koji se pojavi, dajte sigurnu šifru, potvrdite je ponovnim unosom. "
"Pritisnite na <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protected cells in a protected sheet cannot be edited without unprotecting "
"the whole sheet, and any sheet changes are disabled. For example, no one can "
"insert rows or columns, change column width, or create embedded charts."
msgstr ""
"Zaštićene ćelije u zaštićenom listu ne mogu biti uređivane bez skidanja "
"zaštite sa cijelog lista, i sve izmjene na listu su onemogućene. Na primjer "
"niko ne može ubaciti redove ili kolone, promijeniti širinu kolone, ili "
"kreirati ugrađene grafikone."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide cell formula"
msgstr "Sakrij formulu u ćeliji"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might want to hide your formulae so other people cannot see them. By "
"default, every cell is protected and not hidden. But it is important to "
"remember that these attributes have no effect unless the sheet itself is "
"protected."
msgstr ""
"Možda želite sakriti formulu da drugi ljudi ne mogu vidjeti te formule. "
"Zadano svaka ćelija je zaštićena i nije sakrivena. Ali bitno je napomenuti "
"da ovi atributi nemaju efekta ako list nije zaštićen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "A default cell with a formula"
msgstr "Zadana ćelija sa formulom"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To hide cell formulae, select the appropriate cell or range of cells or non-"
"contiguous cells with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> and then "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. In the Cell format dialog, click the "
"<guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> tab and select <guilabel>Hide formula</"
"guilabel>. After you protect the sheet, the results of the formulae will be "
"visible, but the formulae will not."
msgstr ""
"Da sakrijete formulu u ćeliji, odaberite odgovarajući opseg ćelije ili opseg "
"nesusjednih ćelija sa <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> a onda "
"odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Formatiraj "
"ćeliju...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni. U okviru za formatiranje ćelije "
"pritisnite <guilabel>Zaštita ćelije</guilabel> karticu i odaberite "
"<guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel>. Nakon što zaštitite list rezultati "
"formule će biti vidljivi, ali ne i formula."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have now to protect the sheet: choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to display "
"the <guilabel>Protect Sheet</guilabel> dialog box. Enter a safe password "
"twice to prevent others from unprotecting the sheet."
msgstr ""
"Sada morate zaštititi list: odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti list...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za prikaz "
"<guilabel>Zaštita lista</guilabel> okvira. Unesite sigurnu šifru dvaput da "
"spriječite druge da skinu zaštitu sa lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> is enabled and <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> is disabled, the formula is hidden after protecting the sheet but "
"the cell content can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Kada je omogućeno <guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel> i <guilabel>Zaštita</"
"guilabel> onemogućena, formula je sakrivena nakon zaštite lista, ali sadržaj "
"ćelije može biti promijenjen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> is enabled but the cell is not protected "
"and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel> je omogućeno ali ćelija nije zaštićena i "
"list je zaštićen"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> "
"are enabled, the formula is hidden after protecting the sheet and the cell "
"content cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Kada su <guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel> i <guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> "
"omogućeni, formula je sakrivena nakon zaštite lista i sadržaj ćelije ne može "
"biti promijenjen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> are "
"enabled in <guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel> i <guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> se "
"omogućavaju u <guilabel>Zaštita ćelije</guilabel> i list je zaštićen"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that it is very easy to break the password for a protected "
"sheet so if you are looking for real security, this is not the best solution."
msgstr ""
"Zapamtite da je vrlo lahko provaliti šifru za zaštitu lista tako da ako "
"tražite pravu sigurnost ovo nije najbolje riješenje."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide all in the cell"
msgstr "Sakrij sve u ćeliji"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can hide both the formula and the content of the cell by choosing "
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> in the Cell Protection tab in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. In the screenshot below, the cell itself is "
"not protected (<guilabel>Protected</guilabel> is unchecked) thus the cell "
"content can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Možete sakriti i formulu i sadržaj ćeliji ako odaberete <guilabel>Sakrij "
"sve</guilabel> u kartici Zaštita ćelije <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Formatiraj ćeliju...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meniju. "
"U snimci ekrana ispod, ćelija nije zaštićena (<guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> "
"je odznačeno) tako da sadržaj ćelije može biti promijenjen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> only is enabled (no cell protection) and the "
"sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> je samo omogućeno (nema zaštite ćelije) i "
"list je zaštićen"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here the cell itself is protected so it cannot be overwritten."
msgstr "Ovdje je ćelija zaštićena tako da se njen sadržaj ne može izmijeniti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> are enabled "
"in Cell Protection and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> i <guilabel>Zaštićeno</guilabel> su "
"onogućeni u Zaštita ćelije i list je zaštićen"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Ostali dodaci"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Named Cells and Areas"
msgstr "Imenovane ćelije i područja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give a name such as <userinput>foo</userinput> to a cell or to any "
"area of a sheet by selecting the cell or area then selecting <guimenuitem> "
"Area Name...</guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse "
"button menu. This will bring up the <guilabel>Area Name</guilabel> dialog "
"box where you can enter any name you wish."
msgstr ""
"Možete dati me kao na primjer <userinput>foo</userinput> ćeliji ili nekom "
"području lista odabiranjem ćelije ili područja a onda izborom  <guimenuitem> "
"Ime područja...</guimenuitem> iz menija <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> "
"tipke miša. Ovo će prikazati okvir  <guilabel>Ime područja</guilabel> u "
"kojem možete unijeti željeno ime."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also name a cell or area by selecting it then typing the name into "
"the small text box at the left end of the Formula toolbar, overwriting the "
"cell reference that normally appears here."
msgstr ""
"Ćeliju ili područje možete imenovati odabirom istih, a zatim unosom imena u "
"mali tekstualni okvir u lijevom kraju Alatne trake sa formulom, tako da ime "
"upišete umjesto reference ćelije koja tu stoji."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enter a name that has already been used into this text box &sheets;'s "
"selection will change to show the named cell(s)."
msgstr ""
"Ako unesete ime koje je već korišteno u ovaj tekstualni okvir &sheets; "
"odjeljak će promijeniti da prikazuje imenovane ćelije."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Data</guimenu><guimenuitem>Named Areas...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> option will give you a list of existing names and "
"let you change &sheets;'s focus to any of them or let you remove a name."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Podaci</guimenu><guimenuitem>Imenovana područja...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> opcija vam daje listu postojećih imena i "
"dozvoljava promjenu &sheets;-ovog fokusa na neku od njih i dozvoljava vam "
"uklanjanje imena."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Named cells are particularly useful in formulae as an alternative to <link "
"linkend=\"absolute\"> absolute cell references</link> as the names can be "
"used in place of normal cell references and do not change when the cell "
"containing the formula is copied. When a name is used in this way it should "
"be enclosed in single quotation marks."
msgstr ""
"Imenovane ćelije su posebno korisne u formulama kao alternativne  <link "
"linkend=\"absolute\"> apsolutne reference ćelije</link> kao imena mogu biti "
"korištena umjesto normalnih referenci na ćelije i ne mijenjaju se kad se "
"kopira formula. Kada je ime korišteno na ovaj način treba biti označeno "
"jednim navodnicima."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if cell A1 has been given the name <userinput>fred </userinput> "
"then you can enter a formula such as <userinput>='fred' + 2 </userinput> "
"into another cell which would always give the result of adding 2 to the "
"value in A1 no matter where the formula cell was copied to."
msgstr ""
"Na primjer ako ćelija A1 ima ime <userinput>fred </userinput> onda možete "
"unijeti formulu kao <userinput>='fred' + 2 </userinput> u drugu ćeliju koja "
"će uvijek davati rezultat sa dodatim 2 na vrijednost A1 bez obzira gdje je "
"formula kopirana."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that cell and area names are treated as being in lowercase."
msgstr ""
"Primjetite da su imena ćelija i područja tretirana kao ona sa malim slovima."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Comments"
msgstr "Komentari u ćeliji"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A cell can contain a text comment that can be viewed when working on the "
"spreadsheet but which is not printed and not normally seen."
msgstr ""
"Ćelija sadrži tekstualni komentar tako da može biti viđen kada se radi sa "
"tabelom, ali se ne štampa i nije normalno viđen."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a comment select the cell and choose <guimenuitem>Comment...</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button menu or "
"from the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu and type your comment into the "
"resulting <guilabel>Cell Comment</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Da dodate komentar odaberite ćeliju i izaberite <guimenuitem>Komentar...</"
"guimenuitem> iz menija <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke miša ili iz "
"<guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu> menija i unesite vaš komentar u okvir koji se "
"prikaže <guilabel>Komentar u ćeliji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see the comment hover the mouse pointer over the cell. The comment will "
"appear as if it were a Tooltip."
msgstr ""
"Da vidite komentar pređite pokkazivačem preko ćelije. Komentar će se "
"pojaviti kao da je Alatna napomena."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Show comment indicator</guilabel> box of the "
"<guilabel>Sheet Properties</guilabel> dialog, those cells containing "
"comments will be highlighted by a small red triangle in the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"Ako označite <guilabel>Pokaži indikator komentara</guilabel> okvir u "
"<guilabel>Osobine lista</guilabel> okviru, ćelije koje sadrže komentare biće "
"označene malim crvenim trokutom u gornjem desnom uglu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open this dialog, click with the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse "
"button onto the sheet tab at the bottom of the main window and select "
"<guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. Or select "
"it from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Da otvorite ovaj okvir pritisnite <mousebutton>desnom</mousebutton> tipkom "
"miša na karticu lista na dnu glavnog prozora sa <guimenuitem>Osobine lista</"
"guimenuitem> iz skočnog menija. Ili ga odaberite iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>List</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> menija."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a comment from a cell, select <guimenuitem>Remove Comment</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button menu or "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Da uklonite komentar iz ćelije odaberite <guimenuitem>Ukloni komentar</"
"guimenuitem> iz <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke miša menija i "
"odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Očisti</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
